g\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242040/extras/0ef8009eb7d284e1ce250b3511b9d3cd.avif?t=1670523626\" width=616 height=92 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGES</strong></h2>Take on challenges and boast your highest scores.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242040/extras/b126b2ba0fe48589ef9e37bdea4911a1.avif?t=1670523626\" width=446 height=224 /></span>",
